data.description: This house sits on a fantastic large, flat lot. Fenced yard with a swimming pool! Huge front and back porches for relaxing. Inside has the master on the main with another room on the main level that could be a bedroom or an office. Upstairs has two bedrooms with a jack and jill bath and another room that can be a fifth bedroom or make it a playroom or media room. The possibilities are endless.  Main level has a cozy den with a wood burning fireplace, an eat-in kitchen that looks out over the large back yard. Also a spacious laundry room is on the main level.  Main level garage to unload those groceries right into the kitchen. Great flat driveway for those basketball games or bike riding! Newer roof.  New upper level HVAC and main level is newer (both covered under a transferrable warranty).  Come see this one today!
